Spring Leage 2022

Welcome to the location to sign up for Spring League 2022.

If you want to see more details about how the league is going to be run, choose the Home page or click the 3 lines on the top right (if you are on your phone).

General Info

When

Dates: April 25th -> May 30th

  • Mondays from 6:30-8:30pm
  • Multiple games every week!
  • Hanging out after!

Where

Use the following address: Pinetop Sports Club: 3723 Pinetop Rd, Greensboro, NC 27410

Who

You!

What (do you get)

  • 6 weeks of co-ed Ultimate (from April through May) first pull at 630pm, round robin, games to 5.
  • Friends!
